    <p>{`Getting to SFO went fairly smoothly, small crowds, security went fast. So far so good. The good luck kept going on our flight, even with a couple babies sitting around us, we were able to have a pretty enjoyable flight. (As enjoyable as sitting in a cramped chair for 12 hours can be). Food wasn’t bad, our row had extra leg room, the flight attendants assumed we were french (oh-hoh-hoh `}{`<`}{`- french laugh).`}</p>
